column1: # DESCRIPTION: File contains rout speed values for specific materials (from HEG) and specific NC operation.
# Rout speed depands on theses parameters:
# - OPERATIONS: Each tool do some NC operation
# - Tool D: tool diameter in mm
# - Tool Type: - def - default type for this rout operation. Specific tool magazine is selected from MagazineDef.xml
#              - special - Specific tool magazine is selected from MagazineSpec.xml
# - Rout speed INSIDE: Speed for all routs which are detected as rout inside pcb countour
# - Rout speed OUTLINE: Speed for all routs which are detected as countour routing

column3: 40.5: Theses numbers are thicknesses of pcb packet. Thickness of pcb packet depands on minimal rout tool and total order pcb quantity
